"633","ARTICLES SUPPPLEMENTARY TO ARTICLES OF"
"634","INCORPORATION"
"635","In response to Sub-Item 77i(b), Articles of"
"636","Supplementary to Articles of Incorporation, effective as"
"637","of November 12, 2014, of Lord Abbett Affiliated Fund,"
"638","Inc., a Maryland corporation authorized and established"
"639","three new classes of shares; such new classes were"
"640","designated Class R4, Class R5, and Class R6 shares."
"641","The Articles Supplementary is hereby attached as Item"
"642","77Q1(d)."
