"648","<FILENAME>Ex77Q1d.txt"
"649","<DESCRIPTION>SUPPLEMENTAL ARTICLES TO CREATE R4 R5 AND R6 SHARES"
"650","<TEXT>"
"651","			Exhibit 77Q1(d)"
"652","ARTICLES SUPPLEMENTARY"
"653","TO"
"654","ARTICLES OF INCORPORATION"
"655","OF"
"656","LORD ABBETT AFFILIATED FUND, INC."
"657","       LORD ABBETT AFFILIATED"
"658","FUND, INC. (hereinafter called the"
"659","Corporation), a Maryland corporation having"
"660","its principal office c/o The Prentice-Hall"
"661","Corporation System, 7 St. Paul Street, Suite"
"662","1660, Baltimore, Maryland 21202, hereby"
"663","certifies to the State Department of Assessments"
"664","and Taxation of Maryland that:"
"665","       FIRST:  The Corporation presently has"
"666","authority to issue 4,900,000,000 shares of"
"667","capital stock, of the par value $.001 each,"
"668","having an aggregate par value of $4,900,000."
"669","The Board of Directors has previously classified"
"670","and designated 2,900,000,000 authorized shares"
"671","as Class A shares; 300,000,000 authorized"
"672","shares as Class B shares; 300,000,000"
"673","authorized shares as Class C shares;"
"674","300,000,000 authorized shares as Class F"
"675","shares; 300,000,000 authorized shares as Class I"
"676","shares; 200,000,000 authorized shares as Class"
"677","P shares; 300,000,000 authorized shares as"
"678","Class R2 shares; and 300,000,000 authorized"
"679","shares as Class R3 shares."
"680","      SECOND:  In accordance with 2-105(c)"
"681","of the Maryland General Corporation"
"682","Law, the number of shares of capital stock"
"683","which the Corporation shall have authority to"
"684","issue is hereby increased to 5,800,000,000, of"
"685","the par value $.001 each, having an aggregate"
"686","par value of $5,800,000."
"687","       THIRD:  Pursuant to the authority of"
"688","the Board of Directors to classify and reclassify"
"689","unissued shares of stock of the Corporation and"
"690","to classify a series into one or more classes of"
"691","such series, the Board of Directors hereby"
"692","classifies the 900,000,000 newly authorized but"
"693","unclassified and unissued shares as follows:"
"694","300,000,000 shares as Class R4 shares,"
"695","300,000,000 shares as Class R5 shares, and"
"696","300,000,000 shares as Class R6 shares."
"697","       FOURTH:  Subject to the power of the"
"698","Board of Directors to classify and reclassify"
"699","unissued shares, all shares of the Corporation"
"700","hereby classified as specified in Article Third"
"701","above shall be invested in the same investment"
"702","portfolio of the Corporation and shall have the"
"703","preferences, conversion or other rights, voting"
"704","powers, restrictions, limitations as to dividends,"
"705","qualifications, and terms and conditions of"
"706","redemption set forth in Article V of the Articles"
"707","of Incorporation of the Corporation (hereafter"
"708","called the Articles) and shall be subject to all"
"709","other provisions of the Articles relating to stock"
"710","of the Corporation generally."
"711","       FIFTH:  Following the increase in"
"712","authorized shares as specified in Article Second"
"713","above and the classification of authorized but"
"714","unclassified and unissued shares as specified in"
"715","Article Third above, the Corporation has"
"716","authority to issue 5,800,000,000 shares of"
"717","capital stock, of the par value $.001 each,"
"718","having an aggregate par value of $5,800,000."
"719","The authorized shares of the Corporation are"
"720","classified and designated as follows:"
"721","2,900,000,000 authorized shares as Class A"
"722","shares; 300,000,000 authorized shares as Class"
"723","B shares; 300,000,000 authorized shares as"
"724","Class C shares; 300,000,000 authorized shares"
"725","as Class F shares; 300,000,000 authorized"
"726","shares as Class I shares; 200,000,000 authorized"
"727","shares as Class P shares; 300,000,000"
"728","authorized shares as Class R2 shares;"
"729","300,000,000 authorized shares as Class R3"
"730","shares, 300,000,000 shares as Class R4 shares,"
"731","300,000,000 shares as Class R5 shares, and"
"732","300,000,000 shares as Class R6 shares."
"733","       SIXTH:  The Corporation is registered"
"734","as an open-end company under the Investment"
"735","Company Act of 1940.  The total number of"
"736","shares of capital stock that the Corporation has"
"737","authority to issue has been increased by the"
"738","Board of Directors in accordance with 2-105(c)"
"739","of the Maryland General Corporation"
"740","Law.  The shares of stock of the Corporation"
"741","hereby classified as specified in Article Third"
"742","above have been duly classified by the Board of"
"743","Directors under the authority contained in the"
"744","Articles."
"745","       SEVENTH:	Pursuant to 2-208.1(d)(2)"
"746","of the Maryland General Corporation Law, the"
"747","articles supplementary to the Articles set forth"
"748","herein shall become effective on November 12, 2014."
"749","       IN WITNESS WHEREOF, the Corporation has"
"750","caused these presents to be signed in its name"
"751","and on its behalf by its Vice President and"
"752","Secretary and witnessed by its Vice President"
"753","and Assistant Secretary on November 7, 2014."
